name: WAGMI Game
public_notice: WAGMI Game has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. Visit this post for more information and visit the old token page here.
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
For an extensive deep dive on the project, check out our Whitepaper: https://wagmi-games.gitbook.io/wagmi-games-whitepaper

What makes your project unique?
One of the FIRST FIAT TO NFT Mobile Tower Defense Game, incorporating the power of Web3 whilst taking a Web2 onboarding approach.

What’s next for your project?
A detailed Roadmap for the project is available here: https://wagmigame.io/roadmap.html

What can your token be used for?
Discover $WAGMIGAMES Utility! For a deep dive on the token, its utility, and its advantages, check out https://www.wagmigame.io/token.html.
